  "keyFeatures": [
    "Circuit breaker with automatic failure detection and three-state (closed/open/half-open) management",
    "Token bucket rate limiting with per-request, per-client, and global configuration",
    "PCI-compliant logging with automatic sanitization of sensitive data (credit cards, auth tokens, etc.)",
    "Smart retries with exponential backoff, jitter, and Retry-After header support",
    "Request deduplication to prevent duplicate side effects from race conditions or double-clicks",
    "Comprehensive telemetry events via Elixir's :telemetry library",
    "Multi-adapter support: Finch (default), Req, and Tesla",
    "Pre-built configuration profiles for payment processing, high-volume APIs, and microservices mesh",
    "Test mode that blocks real HTTP requests with adapter-agnostic mock utilities",
    "Correlation IDs for distributed tracing and request tracking"
  ],
